overview: "Hong Kong Synergy 24 Drum Competition" is in fact the Part II of the Hong Kong Drum Festival. This production features the wonderful performance of many of the drum ensembles from China Mainland and Hong Kong.  Performers: Shanxi Jiangzhou Drum Troupe Yonghong Peace DrumTroupe of Lanzhou Drum Lead Player: Yim Hok-man The Champion Team of Hong Kong Synergy 24 Drum Competition HKCO
title: Majestic Drum II
